parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents, and also result in inconvenience and frustration for the driver.
symptoms: The radio turns on loudly by itself
the volume control malfunctions
the USB port stops working or shorts out
the infotainment system reboots randomly
the audio system cuts out or fails to produce sound
the system requires frequent rebooting to function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning AEB system can lead to a failure to detect potential collisions, increasing the risk of accidents, and can also cause unnecessary warnings and distractions while driving.
symptoms: The AEB warning light stays on and won't turn off
the system fails to detect potential collisions
the system provides false warnings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected activation of the automatic braking system can cause the vehicle to abruptly stop, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or even fatalities, especially when driving at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly stops without warning
the ABS light illuminates on the dashboard
the braking system activates without any obstacles or vehicles in the vicinity
the vehicle experiences unexplained braking or deceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine oil leaks and failure can cause the engine to seize, leading to costly repairs or even engine replacement, and potentially causing accidents due to loss of power or stalling.
symptoms: Oil level warning light illuminates
smoke appears under the hood
low or no oil in the engine
engine smoke continues after adding oil.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intake gasket failure can cause engine oil leaks, leading to engine damage and potentially causing accidents due to loss of power or stalling.
symptoms: Oil level warning light illuminates
smoke appears under the hood
low or no oil in the engine
engine smoke continues after adding oil.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Spark plug failure can cause engine misfires, leading to decreased engine performance and potentially causing accidents due to loss of power or stalling.
symptoms: Engine misfires
decreased engine performance
rough engine idle.
